    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      554.23,
      555.05,
      609.91
    ],
    "text": "Issued at 04.00 p.m. on 12 April 2026. Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central, Southern, North-western and Uva provinces and in Ampara, Batticaloa and Polonnaruwa districts after 1.00 p.m.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0,
      12.479999542236328,
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      613.21,
      554.96,
      650.59
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers may occur at some places in Hambantota, Ampara, Batticaloa and Monaragala districts in the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      654.37,
      555.05,
      692.74
    ],
    "text": "Fairly heavy falls about 75 mm are likely at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central, Southern and Uva provinces.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      696.16,
      378.98,
      716.62
    ],
    "text": "Mainly dry weather will prevail over the other parts of the island.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      724.93,
      555.05,
      758.74
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central, Sabaragamuwa, Uva and Northern provinces and in Kurunegala district during the early hours of the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      2.0399999618530273,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      762.04,
      554.62,
      799.42
    ],
    "text": "The general public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by temporary localized strong winds and lightning during thundershowers.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      802.84,
      554.76,
      958.08
    ],
    "text": "On the apparent northward relative motion of the sun, it is going to be directly over the latitudes of Sri Lanka during 05th to 15th of April in this year. The nearest areas of Sri Lanka over which the sun is overhead tomorrow (13th) are Pesalai, Mankulam and Nedunkerny about 12:11 noon.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
